land 17-5 in pool play on Wednesday, the Blitzboks hit back in style on Thursday to cause a big upset and ensure they will be playing for a medal at the Stade de France on Saturday.\", \"from\": 542, \"to\": 746, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 558, \"end\": 569, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999992346602, \"rank\": 7.554857509413485e-10, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"pool play\", \"from\": 578, \"to\": 587}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 591, \"to\": 600}, {\"ngram\": \"the Blitzboks\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 615}, {\"ngram\": \"style\", \"from\": 628, \"to\": 633}, {\"ngram\": \"Thursday\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 645}, {\"ngram\": \"a big upset\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 666}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 710}, {\"ngram\": \"the Stade de France\", \"from\": 714, \"to\": 733}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday\", \"from\": 737, \"to\": 745}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Blitzboks' semi-final against France is scheduled for 15:30 on Saturday afternoon (SA and France time).\", \"from\": 748, \"to\": 855, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 782, \"end\": 788, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999919664333, \"rank\": 8.032722920381323e-09, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 835, \"end\": 837, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0601134943830777e-22, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 842, \