\": \"Our defence had been good but we could not get the ball back.\", \"from\": 1181, \"to\": 1242, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our defence\", \"from\": 1181, \"to\": 1192}, {\"ngram\": \"the ball\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1236}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Tonight our defence system worked well and when we had ball in hand we capitalised.\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1328, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our defence system\", \"from\": 1253, \"to\": 1271}, {\"ngram\": \"ball\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1304}, {\"ngram\": \"hand\", \"from\": 1308, \"to\": 1312}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We even left one or two tries out there.\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1369, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one or two tries\", \"from\": 1342, \"to\": 1358}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was still not a perfect performance, but the guys fought for the system, they fought for the jersey and they fought for the country.\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1505, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a perfect performance\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1408}, {\"ngram\": \"the guys\", \"from\": 1414, \"to\": 1422}, {\"ngram\": \"the system\", \"from\": 1434, \"to\": 1444}, {\"ngram\": \"the jersey\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1472}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1504}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am really proud of them and they deserve to be in the semi-finals.\\\"\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1575, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the semi\", \"from\": 1558, \"to\": 1566}, {\"ngram\": \"finals\", \"from\": 1567, \"to\": 1573}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rosko Specman, who scored one of the tries, said afterwards that they did what was needed to stay in the hunt for a podium finish.\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1707, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1577, \"end\": 1582, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rosko\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.98607913667413e-13, \"text\": \"Rosko\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \