"to\": 1841}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We had some ball to play with and it was joy all over.\", \"from\": 1881, \"to\": 1936, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some ball\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 1898}, {\"ngram\": \"joy\", \"from\": 1923, \"to\": 1926}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are still in the tournament and that is a huge boost of confidence.\\\"\", \"from\": 1937, \"to\": 2008, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the tournament\", \"from\": 1953, \"to\": 1967}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge boost\", \"from\": 1980, \"to\": 1992}, {\"ngram\": \"confidence\", \"from\": 1996, \"to\": 2006}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tristan Leyds added: \\\"We had a tough chat with the boys last night and knew we had to pull it together.\", \"from\": 2010, \"to\": 2113, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2010, \"end\": 2017, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tristan\", \"score\": 0.8724665886853766, \"rank\": 0.14567408188137432, \"text\": \"Tristan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tristan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tristan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a tough chat\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2051}, {\"ngram\": \"the boys\", \"from\": 2057, \"to\": 2065}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Japan (who they beat 49-5 earlier on Thursday) was a good start.\", \"from\": 2115, \"to\": 2180, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2116, \"end\": 2121, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9782355802619602, \"rank\": 0.022198253522051625, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_rugby_union_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Thursday\", \"from\": 2153, \"to\": 2161}, {\"ngram\": \"a good start\", \"from\": 2167, \"to\": 2179}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We just knew we had to gain some points on the board and get a victory.\", \"from\": 2181, \"to\": 2252, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some points\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2220}, {\"ngram\": \"the board\", \"from\": 2224, \"to\": 2233}, {\"ngram\": \"a victory\", \"from\": 2242, \"to\": 2251}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We got a second chance against New Zealand and the boys produced a special performance in defence.\\\"\", \"from\": 2253, \"to\": 2352, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2284, \"end\": 2295, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999992346602, \"rank\": 7.554857509413485e-10, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a second chance\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2275}, {\"ngram\": \"the boys\", \"from\": 2300, \"to\": 2308}, {\"ngram\": \"a special performance\", \"from\": 2318, \"to\": 2339}, {\"ngram\": \"defence\", \"from\": 2343, \"to\": 2350}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"People back home did not think we had a chance but where there is a will, there is a way.\", \"from\": 2354, \"to\": 2444, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"People\", \"from\": 2355, \"to\": 2361}, {\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 2393, \"to\": 2401}, {\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 2438, \"to\": 2443}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And the guys put it together and got the 'W' against New Zealand.\\\"\", \"from\": 2445, \"to\": 2511, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2498, \"end\": 2509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999992346602, \"rank\": 7.554857509413485e-10, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the guys\", \"from\": 2449, \"to\": 2457}, {\"ngram\": \"the 'W\", \"f